---
title: Tofu Pad See Ew with Ginger Sugar Snap Peas and Thai Basil
description: Pad See Ew is one of the most popular Thai noodle dishes. It uses wide rice noodles to soak up a sweet soy-based sauce! Flavoured with ginger, garlic, and Thai basil, this stir-fry packs a lot of delicious taste.
